instalar SO en raspberry (sin escritorio)
instalr git (sudo apt update; sudo apt upgrade; sudo apt -y upgrade; sudo apt -y install git)
instalar pyenv (manual en internet)(https://github.com/pyenv/pyenv?tab=readme-ov-file#unixmacos)
generar ssh key, en raspberry (ssh-keygen)
agregar la key a github, para poder clonar los repositorios
instalar redis-server (sudo apt-get install redis-server)
crear un ambiente virtual 3.11 (https://roylans.dev/entorno-virtual-en-python-pyenv)
instalar paquetes python necesarios: rpi.gpio, redis==2.10.5, cronus
instalar en python del sistema (sudo pip3 install redis --break-system-packages; sudo pip3 install cronus --break-system-packages)
crear repositorio
actualizar codigo
vcgencmd measure_temp
agregar pines a pines.py
agregar pines a test.py
agregar pines a read_redis.py

